summary: My preset of my character, hope you guys enjoy!
descriptionHtml:
[font=Arial][size=3][center]Hello everyone, and today I will present you my character Alesa![/center]

[/size][/font][center][font=Arial][size=3]I'm new to modding here, so please tell me if there are any issues!
And most of all, ask any questions you like. ( Hopefully I'll be able to know them)
I have exported the nif head of her just in case you want to use it. 

Installation (Manually) 
Download the j.slot manually, and then download the recommend mods, "if you so choose".
Go to your Skyrim folder and then go to Data/SKSE/Chargen/Presets/ and then put it in the presets.
Open up the console command panel and type in "showracemenu" and then go to the presets tab and load Alesa3.

Required Files
